{"tid":258492,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］點解日日都有隻黑蜜峰走入黎？","createTime":"2017-05-26T07:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T05:39:55.000Z","uid":22244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0da494c706ee9db4a42953d6a04c621b227ba2","tid":258492,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"屋企近排一到下就一至兩點就有隻黑色蜜峰走入我屋企飛黎飛去<br />\n但每次飛入黎又搵窗出返去，好撚無謂<br />\n咁日日飛入黎又搵路飛返出去，係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會聽日同樣鐘數我可以影低隻峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caea17d8d22dd557bb3caadeed8c2590f0f203bc","tid":258492,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"視察環境<br />\n到時會唔只一隻入黎"},{"pid":"61a51e868267974560fdf77a630594adbc8637fd","tid":258492,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:25:12.000Z","msg":"係咪有枝蜜糖爆左？<br />\n之前屋企打爛左枝 啲蜜蜂就日日黎開party"},{"pid":"362deadf39b15f262efdccb94905f16ea0a3ecc5","tid":258492,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"先人嚟"},{"pid":"62257c6df4148cf3ee72a59542961d5efd1b0dd4","tid":258492,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>視察環境<br />\n到時會唔只一隻入黎</blockquote><br />\n我晏d會照下出面窗下面係咪有峰巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f909645bb5c1c5b50cc2765c10575f267d563b","tid":258492,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有枝蜜糖爆左？<br />\n之前屋企打爛左枝 啲蜜蜂就日日黎開party</blockquote><br />\n有蜜糖，但好密封<br />\n之前用開都冇峰入黎"},{"pid":"348f9d72ffbc32bbcb6f28d789c318d0465a2cac","tid":258492,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先人嚟</blockquote><br />\n我細佬都有咁講<br />\n我想問係死左好耐既先人定係岩岩死？"},{"pid":"3fc7e438e29737c6f648ddd5a493